[{"Code":"en","Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl3-k898i9-236\"><a id=\"_6v9tus6b93a9\" display=\"false\"></a></p><h2 data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl6-db84ci-237\"><a id=\"_lxwfvepzuda1\" display=\"false\"></a>PEP</h2><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl6-khc2mu-239\">PEP (Politically Exposed Person) Screening is an important aspect of Anti-Money Laundering and KYC regulation. It involves validating merchant’s identity to determine if they are a PEP.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl6-rbsq0i-240\">During account activation, MO will perform screening of the directors, shareholder  and commissioner* names of our prospect client against PEP name list and found the name matches with the list. </p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl6-02pn04-241\">ComplyAdvantage is a new screening tool used by MO (replacing KYC6) for  screening merchants and its connected parties (such as Authorized Signatories, all Directors, and all UBOs) against sanctions, PEP, and adverse media databases.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl6-318bwd-242\">Screening forms a crucial part of our KYC/CDD procedures to ensure that we protect Xendit from sanction, regulatory, and reputation risks.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl6-0v3ng7-243\"><a id=\"_xhqm4qka69r7\" display=\"false\"></a>Screening</h2><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl6-6xzbfe-245\">ComplyAdvantage (CA), has a total of 7 Production Environments. Each country would have its own environment, and also have 1 environment for Regional Merchants.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl6-qyq8x3-246\">In general, we need to login to CA to review the screening results, which include:<br type=\"inline\"></p><ul data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl7-g38egj-248\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl7-13qowu-249\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4a0-ynworx-734\">Adding notes to each PROFILE to determine if it is a true positive hit or not.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl7-4ggmfi-250\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4a0-hi6emv-735\">Add a status to each PROFILE</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl7-wpn4zb-251\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4a0-3ac79k-736\">Once all PROFILES have been reviewed, change the status of CASE.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl7-xwqpz4-252\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbijep-kfpvmi-475\">If there are hits you are not certain or there are true positive hits, escalate the case to the relevant Money Laundering Reporting Office for each country via #compliance-request channel.</p><ul data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl7-g38egj-248\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkbigyi-cabrwu-474\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl7-2e8nz6-254\">PH: <a><u>Phot Chavez, Louis Marshall Lo</u></a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbilrl-usmgtd-477\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl7-7lmqfp-255\">ID: @compliance-id</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbipx3-k6b9bv-479\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl7-u80pgb-256\">TH: <a><u>Hong Jie Lim</u></a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbis0m-t6hyws-481\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl7-jcfi5c-257\">SG: <a><u>Yanyong David Lin, Ellyaty Priyanka</u></a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbitpp-ufcfg3-483\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl7-2fq4cs-258\">MY: <a><u>Hong Jie Lim</u></a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbivev-wdy66z-485\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl7-ed46ww-259\">VN (if any): <a><u>Hong Jie Lim</u></a></p></li></ul></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl7-t0irwi-260\">Key concept used in CA mesh: </p><ol data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl7-zij301-262\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl7-hhwuk0-263\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4a0-eldi66-737\">Customer : a person or company that has direct relationship with the company</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl7-d0sqvm-264\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4a1-2l7ilu-738\">Customer Screening : a way to ensure and checking the customer against a global database of Sanction, Warning, Fitness and Probity and Watchlist, Politically Exposed Person registered (PEPs) and Adverse Media</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl7-2hey9g-265\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4a1-x4szwp-739\">Customer Monitoring : Continuously checking for a person or company for changes in a potential risk</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl7-5xaiok-266\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4a1-tcjryw-740\">Cases : Once MO creates a search and it has a potential match (hit), then MO creates a case, and continues to look through the CA dashboard and decide whether a profile hit may be a false positive (not an accurate match) or a true positive (an accurate match). </p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl7-sy5ghd-267\">A profile hit is when the customer appears to match somebody in a risk category such as politically exposed persons (PEPs), sanctions or adverse media. </p><ol data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl7-8gy4gh-268\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl7-3r9qnv-269\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4a1-ynjzeb-741\">Alerts : is a signal that gives us an alert during screening or creates a case, so MO needs to check that alert and make a decision on the case. </p></li></ol><h3 data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl7-zqamfs-270\"><a id=\"_8etlhu1gkbg1\" display=\"false\"></a>What needs to be screened?</h3><ul data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl8-nrv7sq-272\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl8-4zn3re-273\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4a1-jrsoxv-742\">Name of Directors</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl8-f0y8sb-274\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4a1-su5jtz-743\">Name of UBOs</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl8-e10jm9-275\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4a1-cfm4hw-744\">Name of All Offices</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl8-idqs6k-276\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4a1-jj6bng-745\">Name of Shareholders</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl8-xrsj72-277\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4a1-ollyf1-746\">Name of Entity that is onboarding</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl8-rwvo8p-278\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4a1-9wxbju-747\">Name of Entities that are shareholders</p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl8-6kw2je-279\"><a id=\"_oi057xfna7jw\" display=\"false\"></a>Environments</h3><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl8-6weoyo-281\">Name of Environment</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl9-wsgy63-282\">What is included in this scope</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl9-1tpqbn-283\">Regional Environment</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl9-3y1k0c-284\">Merchants that are onboarding with more than 1 Xendit market</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl9-t9sfic-285\">ID Environment</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl9-p244g4-286\">Merchant that are onboarded in from Indonesian dashboard </p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl9-n1t27c-287\">PH Environment</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl9-492id8-288\">Merchant that are onboarded in from Philippines dashboard </p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h3 data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl9-34o4e1-289\"><a id=\"_mo4msejv1b2y\" display=\"false\"></a>Statuses</h3><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl9-dz8kp0-290\">Name of Status</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfl9-22du6g-291\">What this mean</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfla-qdxijx-292\">In Review</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfla-0yicz6-293\">Onboarding teams agents have not decided on the “trueness” of the match; it could mean:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mmkbhfla-av0g5t-294\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhfla-o9v6ea-295\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4a3-a9e14w-748\">Merchant Operations is checking with merchants; asking for IDs or other additional documents to verify</p></li></ul></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfla-jxqvvx-296\">True Positive</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfla-7bez7b-297\">The merchant’s identity is indeed the same identity as the person or entity who is listed as a PEP, Sanctioned Individual, Adverse FInding subject, etc on ComplyAdvantage</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfla-no2wwy-298\">False Positive</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfla-uohcc2-299\">The merchant turns out to not be a hit (PEP, Sanctioned Individual, Adverse FInding subject, etc).</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfla-q861tq-300\">Example; the merchant has a common name that matches a different individual who is the actual PEP, Sanctioned individual, etc</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mmkbhfla-a70qey-301\"><a id=\"_iuyamiajkt0l\" display=\"false\"></a>Screening Flow</h2><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfla-ifu8hu-302\">To perform screening on ComplyAdvantages, please follow this guideline: </p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:50px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfla-6t2mai-303\">No</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfla-o4ool0-304\">Step</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfla-ql7cmo-305\">Who</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflb-ifymuf-306\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflb-y5ol0t-307\">Login to CA dashboard <a href=\"https://ca-platform-prod.eu.auth0.com/u/organization?state=hKFo2SBCVlN3bk1zS3k1N3VVbXVvc1lDc1NiRkNYMHYzZllPbqFur3VuaXZlcnNhbC1sb2dpbqN0aWTZIDVuWlhWNWxDdFhHS05salJTS2RHdXdyb1Z6cGZnYURXo2NpZNkgUG5XdXdyYjJKcnpJUXMxRXJCdGRTT3ZXYUoyT1VNdFU\"><u>Here</u></a></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflb-ft9yj1-308\">each MO agent will have login access (if link above not working, use the link from ComplyAdvantage’s email)</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflb-cnswu7-309\">Fill in xendit as company name</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflb-hdyxoz-310\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhflb-0n0t2q-311\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-779me6zy.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflb-99rpx7-312\">enter your email address: </p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflb-ivp9s6-313\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhflb-xrno0r-314\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-2mu8xtmw.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflb-haizdl-315\">Enter your login access and password, and click continue</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflb-ixvvqo-316\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhflb-do2nlk-317\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-h4j4btcl.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflb-ekoh0x-318\">Once you've successfully logged in, you'll see the Cases list page.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflb-27envj-319\">💡Make sure you use Specific Environment (ID/PH/etc)  before create a search</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflb-cgrs2g-320\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhflb-iodjom-321\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-r64w66dn.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflb-5xzz0d-322\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflb-oii7rz-323\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflc-6sbvon-324\">How to create a Search</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflc-4zshjz-325\">In CA dashboard, select Customer in the main header</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflc-w158ru-326\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhflc-o236kc-327\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-y2edyzcv.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflc-6j4tky-328\">select Create, then Create Person</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflc-c51950-329\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhflc-hp6ful-330\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-qnt5yehh.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflc-rul7e0-331\">Fill in the details</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflc-flqvhp-332\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhflc-ocggjc-333\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-xpvpfknk.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflc-pn1zr1-334\">Here is an example of the Create new person form:</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflc-ummsad-335\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhflc-ene69g-336\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-hhph9lqc.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflc-4u30oo-337\">In this section, to create a specific match result , fill in the fields with  as many details as you have, such as : </p><ul data-block-id=\"mmkbhflc-2ghdrk-338\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhflc-tzfz2n-339\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4a7-v82uxb-749\">Complete name</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhflc-93wa6y-340\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4a7-4qjusg-750\">Gender</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhflc-22zd2s-341\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4a7-5yh324-751\">Dob (Date of birth)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhflc-wwa8tw-342\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4a7-d34gmi-752\">Country of birth</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhflc-z3xvwt-343\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4a7-aqil7v-753\">Nationality</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfld-cv93vt-344\">📝 For Customer Identifier, MO need to fill in the detail with merchant’s BID number along with merchant’s detail with template: </p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfld-2cswx7-345\">BID number_name of Director</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfld-4e5kyv-346\">BID number_Shareholder name</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfld-zr3z0n-347\">BID number_Company name (if the company is one of the shareholder)</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfld-epfxli-348\">click Next, and choose Screening configuration type, for MO, choose Regional Merchant Onboarding and click create</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfld-jkysak-349\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhfld-35qr9z-350\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-yice43ef.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfld-celcg5-351\">once it finished on creating search, CA will show you the result, if your profile has no hit below is the result </p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfld-b3fx33-352\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhfld-72ifa3-353\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-uao0ytxi.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfld-k6vl6m-354\">If your profile has a hit, then the result will show you as follows</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfld-d2oj7j-355\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhfld-m1767b-356\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-6m9cq8on.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfld-t78qqs-357\">MO-</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfld-6kn951-358\">3</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfld-srf8rt-359\">How to create a Case</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfld-7yzl2l-360\">A case is created for a profile in ComplyAdvantage Mesh <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1MMdMsqIXKcMdYISpRCezw1JaLYBT0pzS5QpI354A8Bk/edit?tab=t.0#heading=h.8y18dhqp6cnl\"><u>if the profile has a hit</u></a>. The case contains information about the profile, including any alerts raised. An alert is a signal that something suspicious was found.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfld-34k641-361\">Once MO gets the result of the search, and if the profile has many results as listed below, then MO has to  identify whether the profile hit is a true or false positive, this is what we called a Case. </p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfld-wzgsr9-362\">📝 Please refer to this <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1MMdMsqIXKcMdYISpRCezw1JaLYBT0pzS5QpI354A8Bk/edit?tab=t.0#heading=h.8y18dhqp6cnl\"><u>SOP on how handling screening hits</u></a></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfld-4zvo80-363\">By default, the screening result status is Not reviewed.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfld-7x87bp-364\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-9d049n-365\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-fipr0rl0.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-tmltlx-366\">The next step on this stage for MO is to review each result, and make a decision whether it’s a True Positive or False Positive. </p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-uvte6q-367\">Click on a row to open the screening result you want to assign a status to.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-jsi9e8-368\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-dtqwwr-369\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-3gwcgpbp.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-h3vl5s-370\">MO will check and review the information provided and make a decision based on the information on Admindashboard (OM).</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-2aqdbn-371\">Select an option from the Status dropdown.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-4werr6-372\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-7atj74-373\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-k6u567i0.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-pslmk2-374\">The screening result will be updated with the selected status, whether it’s True Positive or False Positive</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-dvakge-375\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-gmj257-376\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-fjj7h5o3.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-0r6fje-377\">If the profile is True Positive, or False Positive, then MO write notes to the profile.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-waslme-378\">Go to the case you want to leave a note on and click the notes icon in the top-right corner.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-a8bxbh-379\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-yeerxj-380\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-b21hf0xh.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-n0aq53-381\">📝What to write under “Notes”</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-7yoi98-382\">The intention of “Notes” is to provide an audit trail demonstrating the thought process of the users working on the case. It is important from a regulatory perspective.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-h6ky3v-383\">Please refer to this document for more details on how to review profiles. </p><ul data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-6jnj9y-384\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-k8aqr9-385\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4a9-6sxzhv-754\">If the Profile turns out to be a true positive hit because you have 2 identifiers that match with the name you have screened, (i.e. primary identifier, NAME, and secondary identifier, DOB, are exact match), you could write down your thought process as “true positive hit as both the name and dob match the director/ubo”. </p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-3ugbfo-386\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4a9-5clpvr-755\">Conversely, if you are certain that the Profile is a false positive because for example the DOB is mismatched or the GENDER is a mismatch, you can write down under “Notes” as “false positive due to mismatch in DOB/GENDER”. </p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-fw1dxv-387\">In the future, the tool might be able for us to templatise some responses. In the meantime, please be clear on your decisions why the Profile is a true or false positive. </p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-zo7q2e-388\"> </p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-kml3nw-389\">On this stage, MO also can change the Stage status, if the profile is True Positive and need to escalate, update the stage on the Change Stage, choose escalated (this will be described on point 4 - <em>How To Escalate</em>)</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-6eis7t-390\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-n4unl2-391\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-aiyuszhf.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-q5xx0k-392\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-c5wzrm-393\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-l9q5yg2w.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-qlzsr5-394\">And the status of the Profile will automatically change to Escalated, this means the profile will be reviewed by L2, and they will make a decision</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-utsxc0-395\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-5y1j98-396\">4</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-7fafkm-397\">How To Escalate (move to different table)</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-gwxa2k-398\">If there are hits and MO not certain or there are true positive hits, escalate the case to the relevant Money Laundering Reporting Officer for each country.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-8nhj43-399\">You can change the stages for a profile case from the case view page, or change the stages for multiple cases using the bulk action option on the case list page. <img data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-p69dtn-400\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-sfoennsl.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-i4mwzh-401\">choose the Stage, and click Change Stage</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-uwekmb-402\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhfle-34893h-403\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-hspmv36k.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-p1e431-404\">For escalation cases, MO needs to assign a case to a specific Reporting Officer (L2). </p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-6xvm0r-405\">Go to section Unassigned, and it will show you list of names for assignee, choose the name of the L2 officer </p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-2u099t-406\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-js8dfc-407\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-1qrm5pl5.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-c7387f-408\">PH: @Guada</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-hqhh5w-409\">ID: @Paramitha Tennes</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-t1ygko-410\">TH: @Olivia Mokarat</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-iof0xb-411\">SG: @delwyn</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-w4n9v3-412\">MY: @hongjie</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-l9ubt5-413\">VN (if any): @hongjie for now.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-8j46fa-414\">If a profile hit True Positive, leave a notes and assign the officer, and the CA dashboard will display as follows </p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-1gk6r6-415\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-d4t2ej-416\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-n2wszkco.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-7hhmg3-417\">The profile will have detail as follows</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-t8yw4w-418\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-wyswuh-419\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-l9sko7po.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-sxczbq-420\">L2 will be notified on CA dashboard, but also for visibility, MO also need to notify L2 on slack, to do this action, MO will use the feature ⚠️ in OM dashboard, MO will use this feature to notify the L2 about ongoing case escalation</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-kgsndo-421\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-bf0upr-422\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-q8yrqvou.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\">on the pop up box, fill in the reference link, tick on the compliance, and click send. </p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-gudmub-423\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-u97anl-424\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-lyf0lkd7.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-pjfsmz-425\">This action will notify the Compliance team on slack, and if the L2 is not mentioned on slack automatically then tag them manually. </p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-4h5qtk-426\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-zvul0m-427\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-3cmeif5s.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-tpq625-428\">L2 will create decision on the profile and MO need to wait for the decision, the decision could be: </p><ul data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-0lvelx-429\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-jnz7k4-430\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4ab-ku6a9o-756\">No Risk - Accept</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-uqv46x-431\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4ab-owzdoo-757\">Manageable Risk - Accept</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-yk6mad-432\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4ab-oytpp3-758\">Unacceptable Risk - Reject</p></li></ul></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-v07e1c-433\">MO - L2</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflf-6zgxu3-434\">5</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-fbsg72-435\">L2 Make a decision</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-poq3ek-436\">Once MO create a case and escalate to Reporting Officer (L2), they will receive notification on CA dashboard and also notified on specific thread on slack, once their name is assigned as assignee from MO, L2 will review a profile and make a decision</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-j8lgmx-437\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-fog2e1-438\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-h35iwhko.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-lynmzf-439\">L2  will review a case profile, and make decision whether the profile is: </p><ul data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-7bjkkm-440\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-1lii6o-441\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4ab-pc95eh-759\">No Risk - Accept</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-wdcnn2-442\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4ac-o47x9p-760\">Manageable Risk - Accept</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-bk6sg4-443\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4ac-7xmqrm-761\">Unacceptable Risk - Reject</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-2n6i3g-444\">Once L2 make a decision, the result will be displayed on profile and MO can proceed accordingly (based on L2 decision), and the CA dashboard will display the case detail as follows: </p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-ax2bnc-445\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-g6cava-446\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-uyx93rpu.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-u6ezj3-447\">MO also can check the case status on the CA dashboard and filter from Case List. By default, the case list page only shows cases that are open. Select Closed cases beside the search box to see closed cases. </p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-fz6ajt-448\">To find a case, enter the customer name or ID associated with the case into the search box. The search results update as you type.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-zfp5zv-449\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-5b7xqg-450\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-7tmzjpjj.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-tcwt1h-451\">The search results update as you type with your search term highlighted</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-lc5m01-452\">💡Quick filters for cases</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-ddl5gf-453\">Always make sure to use the correct environment (ID / PH / Regional) to search a case status, incorrect using an environment will cause invalid results. </p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-arn4j4-454\">You can also use Filters for more options to help narrow your search.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-s2vtvo-455\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-wb3k9h-456\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-yglaq0un.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-zzo5lg-457\">The additional filters enable you to find cases by:</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-j8j001-458\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-syz4au-459\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/sop-merchant-screening-image-6d5763uw.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflg-eowpcc-460\">L2 </p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflh-6awp7o-461\">If a merchant is a true hit (True Positive) → Escalate to Local Compliance using ComplyAdvantage → Compliance inform decision to MO based on decision below: </p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflh-vyc03k-462\">Name of Status</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflh-tr276m-463\">What this mean</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflh-qf8cl7-464\">No Risk - Accept</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mmkbhflh-65xh95-465\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhflh-249stc-466\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4ad-r5igaj-762\">MO agent can set live / onboarding merchant  (after clearance from Compliance)</p></li></ul></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflh-yucsxr-467\">Manageable Risk - Accept</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mmkbhflh-5lgati-468\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhflh-ftzdb4-469\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4ad-c3svk9-763\">MO agent can set live / onboarding merchant with condition (monitoring from compliance)</p></li></ul></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhflh-2q8jrh-470\">Acceptable Risk - Reject</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mmkbhflh-5delfe-471\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkbhflh-n9p502-472\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkbhfll-qz49e6-473\">MO agent reject merchant’s application (merchant not allowed to onboard)</p></li></ul></th></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"mmt0o4ae-noq292-764\"></p>","ContentType":2},{"Code":"id","Content":null,"ContentType":2},{"Code":"th","Content":null,"ContentType":2},{"Code":"es-mx","Content":null,"ContentType":2}]